          from
          %span(itemprop='address' itemscope itemtype='http://schema.org/PostalAddress')
            %span(itemprop='addressLocality') Chicago
      #container
        %article.column
          %h2 About Me

          %p I am a #{ @age } year old web developer living in Chicago.
          %p I love making new things, learning new things, and doing new things. I am probably a so-called “serial hobbyist.”
          %p I take unnatural pleasure in pruning my RSS feeds, removing Facebook friends, and freeing up hard disk space.
          %p I <a href="http://typetees.threadless.com/product/1543/I_can_t_get_enough_minimalism">can’t get enough minimalism</a>.
          %p I am a vegetarian and have been so my entire life. But I do eat fish. I guess that makes me a pescetarian.
          %p I am <em>obsessed</em> with <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Snowboarding">the Shred</a> (and most other boardsports).
          %p I believe that <a href="http://37signals.com/svn/posts/1741-how-you-do-anything-is-how-you-do-everything">how you do anything is how you do everything</a>.
          %p I’m pretty much in love with everything Apple makes; I have a MacBook Pro, an Apple Cinema Display, an iPhone and sometime soon I'll be getting an iPad.
          %p I believe if something is easy it’s probably not worth doing.
          %p <span class="strike">I <a href="http://www.daretorant.com/?p=229">hate IE6</a> and will not develop for it on <a href="http://ie6nomore.com/">principle</a>.</span> I had all knowledge of IE6 removed by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eternal_Sunshine_of_the_Spotless_Mind">Lacuna, Inc.</a> It's better this way.
          %p I believe the <a href="http://37signals.com/svn/posts/1626-the-most-powerful-word-is-no">word “no”</a> is not used nearly often enough.
          %p I really like writing lists.

